sections.heading: Rescinded. 2005, e.o. No. 2005-4, Eff. Feb. 15, 2005.
sections.text: Compiler's Notes:Executive Reorganization Order No. 2000-6 was promulgated on July 28, 2000, as Executive Order No. 2000-9, Eff. Sept. 28, 2000. This Executive Reorganization Order was rescinded by Executive Order No. 2005-4, Eff. Feb. 15, 2005.
